-# Horizontal rule -----------------------------------------------------------
%p The <code>hr</code> element represents a paragraph-level thematic break, e.g. a scene change in a story, or a transition to another topic within a section of a reference book.

-# Example
= featureExample do
  %p #{lorem.paragraph}.
  %hr
  %p #{lorem.paragraph}.
-# /Example

-# Code
= featureCode do
  :numcode
    <p>Content...</p>
    <hr />
    <p>More content...</p>
-# /Code